T02D2096:92b-1: a'arya dzny'a nas tva manydzu shr'i no pi ka n'a ma /
T02D2096:92b-3: 'phags pa 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa'i mngon par rtogs pa zhes bya ba /
T02D2096:92b-4: 'phags pa 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2096:92b-5: sangs rgyas kun gyi mes po ni //
T02D2096:92b-6: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje can //
T02D2096:93a-1: dpal ye shes sems dpa' ni //
T02D2096:93a-2: rgyal ba kun gyi yab gyur te //
T02D2096:93a-3: 'khor los sgyur bcas thams cad kyis //
T02D2096:93a-4: rang gi rigs la bstod byas te //
T02D2096:93a-5: bskyed pa'i rim las rdzogs 'gyur ba'i //
T02D2096:93a-6: brjod dang des brjod bshad par bya //
T02D2096:93a-7: thog mar bsam gtan pas dpen zhid nyams dga' ba'i
T02D2096:93a-8: sa phyogs su cung zhig blo bde bar gnas te
T02D2096:93a-10: de nas rang gi snying gar sa bon gyi yi
T02D2096:93a-11: ge gzi brjid dang ldan pas 'gro ba ma lus
T02D2096:93a-12: pa sbyangs shing dag par yid kyis bltas te /
T02D2096:93a-13: dbyangs kyi yi ges bstod la rjes su bya ba nyid kyis gzhug cing rnam par bsgom par bya'o //
T02D2096:93a-14: de nas 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' 'gro ba'i bla ma dang ldan pa spyan drangs te /
T02D2096:93a-16: de nas sngags kyi phreng ba lan bdun du blangs te /
T02D2096:93a-17: me tog gi mchod pas sangs rgyas kyi dbang bskur
T02D2096:93a-18: ba mi bzad pa gnang bas byin gyis brlabs pa'i
T02D2096:93a-20: de nas yang a'a lis sbyangs te /
T02D2096:93a-21: 'od zer rnon po can dang ldan pa'i bsrung ba'i 'khor lo bya'o //
T02D2096:93a-22: de'i dkyil du sna tshogs pa'i padma shes rab dang
T02D2096:93a-23: thabs yang dag par 'dus pa'i blo gros chen po
T02D2096:93a-24: ye shes kyis mtshan pa'i sa bon las sngar gyi
T02D2096:93a-25: bde bar gshegs pa bla ma dang ldan pa'i tshogs
T02D2096:93a-27: / de dag las skyes pa'i 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' ni zhal gsum pa phyag drug pa //
T02D2096:93a-28: rdo rje skyil mo krung las cung zhig 'gying ba /
T02D2096:93a-29: dkar ba dang sdo zhing dmar ba dang /
T02D2096:93a-30: dmar zhing dkar ba'i mdog can nyi ma dang /
T02D2096:93a-32: autpal blo gros chen pos mtshan pa dang /
T02D2096:93a-35: autpa la rtsa ba dang ldan pa ye shes chen pos mtshan pa'i phyag rgya can /
T02D2096:93a-36: khro ba dang zhi ba mnyam pa'i nyams mnga' ba /
T02D2096:93a-37: rin po che'i rgyan rnam pa sna tshogs pas spras pa /
T02D2096:93a-38: zla ba rgyas pa lta bu bsgom par bya'o //
T02D2096:93a-39: de nas rang gi snying gi'i sa bon gyis 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' 'am /
T02D2096:93a-40: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo chen po spyan drangs te /
T02D2096:93a-41: yang bstod nas rab tu gnas pa dang /
T02D2096:93a-43: byin gyis brlabs pa ni de nyid las yongs su rdzogs par bya'o //
T02D2096:93a-44: de nas yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi snang ba thob nas /
T02D2096:93a-45: mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i bstod pa bya'o //
T02D2096:93b-1: yang skad cig gis 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpar dmigs te /
T02D2096:93b-2: rang gi sa bon las spyan drangs nas /
T02D2096:93b-3: aa dang re pha las gyur pa'i shes rab dang
T02D2096:93b-4: thabs 'dus byas pa'i dbus su yi ge mu dmar
T02D2096:93b-6: gcig tu gyur pa'i bcom ldan 'das nam mkha'i khams
T02D2096:93b-7: su bzhugs su gsol te stegs bu dri zhim pa
T02D2096:93b-8: rin po che'am / me tog gis gcal bkram pa'i steng du glegs bam bzhag la /
T02D2096:93b-9: sardza rardza la sogs pa btul te /
T02D2096:93b-10: lkog ma sbyang ba byas nas /
T02D2096:93b-11: mtshan yang dag par brjod pa bklag par bya'o //
T02D2096:93b-12: de nas yan lag bdun pa byas la /
T02D2096:93b-13: yang sngar bzhin sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dbang bskur ba rin po che thob nas ;
T02D2096:93b-14: / lhan cig skyes pa'i rnal 'byor la gnas par bya'o //
T02D2096:93b-15: 'di dag gi rnal 'byor ni zhal gsum dkar zhing zhi ba dang /
T02D2096:93b-16: phyag bzhi pa nyi ma dang zla ba yangs pa'o //
T02D2096:93b-17: yid la mi byed pa'i rnal 'byor glegs bam gyi
T02D2096:93b-18: go 'phang dang ldan pa rnams kyis ni brag ca
T02D2096:93b-19: lta bu'i kha ton bya ste /
T02D2096:93b-21: bdag gis mngon par rtogs pa 'dis /
T02D2096:93b-22: blun po rnams ni blo 'phel zhing //
T02D2096:93b-23: blo gros can rnams bde rnyed nas //
T02D2096:93b-24: ye shes sems dpa'i gnas 'gyur shog / rin chen
T02D2096:93b-25: rgyud rgyal 'di ni sa phyogs gang na gnas pa
T02D2096:93b-26: dang // 'don cing klog par byed pa'i skyes bu de nyid ni //
T02D2096:93b-27: yid bzhin nor bu brgya byin gcug na gnas pa bzhin //
T02D2096:93b-28: bdud rnams zil gnon 'jigs pa thams cad bde bar 'gyur //
T02D2096:93b-29: 'phags pa 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa'i mngon par rtogs pa zhes bya ba //
T02D2096:93b-30: rgya gar gyi mkhan po dpal ldan gnyis su med pa'i rdo rjes mdzad pa /
